PJX, v 1.2.1
API Specification

Nassib Nassar  
Etymon Systems, Inc.

This document is the API specification for PJX.

See:
          Description

PJX
com.etymon.pjx The fundamental classes for creation and modification of PDF documents.
com.etymon.pjx.stream Provides methods for encoding and decoding PDF streams.
com.etymon.pjx.util Utility classes for performing common functions on PDF documents.

 

This document is the API specification for PJX. This API requires J2SE 1.4.0 or later.

Please note that deprecated methods and classes are planned for removal in future versions unless stated otherwise. This API is work in progress and subject to change.

Additional information is available from the PJX web page at http://www.etymon.com/pjx/ or via e-mail at info@etymon.com, or by contacting:
